metadata.name: Blue-Red-White
metadata.description:
🌎 During my last trip to Julfa city, I had the opportunity to shoot this collection.
Julfa is located between Armenia, Azerbaijan, and Iran along the Aras River. 
As a result of the political and economic situation in the region, it is not permitted to take photos. However, it took a lot of coordination to photograph the fantastic architecture of this area.

🏅Despite having been taken less than a month ago, this collection won second place in a prestigious national photo festival.

📸Date Taken: May 2022

🏙Dimensions: 3945 × 2630
